{"tid":1660923,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"A Step-by-Step Guide to Registering an LIHKG Account","createTime":"2019-10-17T21:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T19:02:44.000Z","uid":253377,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ebc1a41ff2e8668183a1ef73295b5fbd841578e","tid":1660923,"uid":253377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:56:32.000Z","msg":"Hi World,<br />\n<br />\nLooks like some of you are interested in registering for an LIHKG account. Welcome to the family.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />In case some of you do not read Chinese, here's a guide:<br />\n<br />\n1. On the pop-up menu on the left hand side, click this: <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQsXUOO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQsXUOO.png&h=1a0bc1bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. Click on register: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1vTgqW2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1vTgqW2.png&h=8a29ce8c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n3. Register! Remember you can only apply for an account with an ISP or college email.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGFOg5u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGFOg5u.png&h=afd20c44&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n4. You will receive a confirmation email in your ISP / college email. Click on the confirmation link.<br />\n5. Welcome to LIHKG<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNote: It looks like there's only a Chinese version of the captcha bot test. Use Google Translate for that so you know which images to click on."},{"pid":"b9f3251905da567c5ec7ab624fffcb6c1b6e9e4e","tid":1660923,"uid":10726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辛苦哂巴打<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks so much bro"},{"pid":"d250ad69792e888bf1c03298852d92ae27decf7c","tid":1660923,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T22:29:53.000Z","msg":"外國isp 好似用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b11a924a1494414ff6c7fa078db88c9a4620dc","tid":1660923,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T22:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a379807251f1c103e658162fca64fb48c489c85","tid":1660923,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d250ad69792e888bf1c03298852d92ae27decf7c","tid":1660923,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T22:29:53.000Z","msg":"外國isp 好似用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T23:03:21.000Z","msg":"一定要香港"},{"pid":"77b3aaf91de9e1356090dfa468d99aea2cdf9f99","tid":1660923,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:02:44.000Z","msg":"WHEN WOULD PRIMARK ESTABLISH BRANCHES IN HONG KONG REGION<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}